{"word":"ὁμηρεύω","slug":"ὁμηρεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὁμηρεύω</b></el> <el>(ὁμηρεύω,) ( φυτ. <el>-σω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ὅμηρος'><el>ὅμηρος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be</i> or <i>serve as a hostage</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:transitive'>trans.</a> <i>to give as a hostage</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}